<section class="panel panel-default">
    <header class="panel-heading">
        <h4 class="panel-title"><a name="Pyramid"></a>Venue details</h4>
    </header>
    <div class="panel-body">
        <h4 class="mrgn-tp-0">Location and parking: </h4>
        <p>Pyramid Island is located 7.5 km from the Jasper townsite. There are only 5 parking stalls at the trailhead and a shared parking lot about 100m to the entry point. This is a public area that can be very busy during the peak season months (June &ndash; September). Shuttle services for larger groups are highly recommended. </p>
        <h4>Amenities:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Bench seating for 50 people </li>
            <li>Million dollar view! </li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Group size: </h4>
        <p>Maximum number of people for this site is 50.</p>
        <!--<p>A maximum group size of 30 people has been set for this site due to the requirements for physical distancing and the size of the venue. This new maximum will be in place while the requirement for physical distancing is in place.</p>
    <p>All gatherings must follow the requirement for physical distancing and <a href="https://www.alberta.ca/restrictions-on-gatherings.aspx">Alberta&rsquo;s provincial restrictions on gatherings</a> in place at the time of their event.</p>-->
        <h4>Time slots and fees: </h4>
        <div class="alert alert-info">
            <p>A non-refundable administration fee of $13.50 applies to every reservation. </p>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>10:30 am - 11:30&nbsp;am ($49)</li>
            <li>11:30 am &ndash; 12:30&nbsp;pm ($49)</li>
            <li>12:30 pm &ndash; 1:30&nbsp;pm ($49)</li>
            <li>1:30 pm&nbsp;&ndash; 2:30 pm ($49)</li>
            <li>2:30 pm&nbsp;&ndash; 3:30&nbsp;pm ($49)</li>
            <li>3:30 pm&nbsp;&ndash; 4:30 pm ($49)</li>
            <li>4:30 pm&nbsp;&ndash; 5:30 pm ($49)</li>
            <li>5:30 pm&nbsp;&ndash; 6:30 pm ($49)</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> You may book up to a maximum of 3 time slots.</p>
        <h4>General information: </h4>
        <ul>
            <li>This is a day use only area (no overnight stay or camping) </li>
            <li>Length of booking will need to include time for set-up and clean-up </li>
            <li>The general area remains publicly accessible and users are not to block off parking spots or trail access </li>
            <li>Users are responsible for area clean-up following their event </li>
            <li>Fires are not permitted at this location </li>
            <li>This day use area should only be used for the ceremony (and pictures). Extended stays or receptions are not appropriate.</li>
            <li>This is a public area, so the consumption of liquor is prohibited.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For any additional information, please contact: <span aria-hidden="true" class="fas fa-envelope"></span> <a href="mailto:groupesjasper-jaspergroups@pc.gc.ca">jaspergroups@pc.gc.ca</a></p>
    </div>
</section>
